title: Bombshell Series by Rip Curl - Made for Surfing
description:
Alana Blanchard and Nikki van Dijk hit the north coast of NSW to put our new Bombshell Series range to the test. Let's just say, they passed! Made for Surfing, Designed with Style, surf comfortable in Rip Curl's Bombshell Series range.

Artist: Anomura
Track: So
